535
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:29,000
And this Feynman diagram,

536
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:31,000
among other things,

537
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:33,000
controls,

538
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:35,000
it's first of all,

539
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:37,000
among other things,

